title: Kiss - 1974-04-01 - Cleveland, OH (FM Broadcast) FLAC
description:
KISS
Cleveland, OH 4/1/74
Agora Theatre
FM Broadcast

Discovered back in December of 2011 via our KISS8mmfilms youtube page. This great recording marks 
the very first known FM Broadcast. No edits, cuts or EQ. This is exactly how we received.

1) Deuce
2) Strutter
3) Cold Gin
4) She - Ace Frehley Solo
5) Firehouse
6) Nothin' To Lose
7) 100,000 Years
8) Black Diamond
